          <title>Trump spars with Maine's governor at the White House over transgender athletes</title>
          <description><![CDATA[President Donald Trump sparred with Maine's Democratic governor during a meeting of governors at the White House on Friday, with Gov. Janet Mills telling the Republican president, “We'll see you in court,” over his push to deny federal funding to the state over transgender athletes.]]></description>
